Peter Zaffino (born January 1967) is an insurance industry leader and executive, named EVP and Global Chief Operating Officer of AIG in July 2017.[1]
Prior to his appointment at AIG, Zaffino served as chief executive officer of Marsh, and chairman of Marsh & McLennan Companies' Risk & Insurance Services segment, which includes Marsh, a risk advisor and insurance broker, and Guy Carpenter and Company, a reinsurance intermediary.[2]



